column5: ....Super, while I haven't read all the reports yet it's apparent I missed another great OFC G2G'er.
Looks like a good time was had by all. Dawg needs to get some sun he looks a pasty white color that just aint right.  Art

Great report as always Joey..... YouNPaul had another exellent adventure and another one enjoyed by us reading it. We couldnt see all the pics with the service we get out here for the 'puter but we could just imagine.
Great to see you and Paul again! Despite our surroundings and slow fishing a great time was had by all. That's what these GTG's are all about! Hope to see you again soon! -Brian
Awesome report girl thanks for the shirt .Beauty fish  I missed out on yer beef jerky but the shrimp you brought to the potluck were also very tasty.
